/* This module is used to store and manage the license
Key locally and persistently */


LICENSE KEY MANAGEMENT LOCALLY
================================================

1) ADD NEW KEY
=================================================
	$ python key_management.py -k <key>
	
		OR
	$ python key_management.py --key <key>

2) LIST DOWN THE KEY STATUS
=================================================
	$ python key_management.py -l


3) GET THE KEY
=================================================
	$ python key_management.py -g

4) DELETE THE KEY
==================================================
	$ python key_management.py -d <key>

5) ADD POOL OF KEYS FROM FILE
==================================================
    $ python key_management -f <file_name_containing_keys>

    Note :- file contain only keys one per line.

